+
+$ sudo systemctl restart sshd.service</fixtext><fix id="F-32974r567737_fix" /><check system="C-32999r567736_chk"><check-content-ref href="Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux_8_STIG.xml" name="M" /><check-content>Verify that unattended or automatic logon via ssh is disabled with the following command:
