+
+The audit daemon must be restarted for the changes to take effect.</fixtext><fix id="F-33109r568142_fix" /><check system="C-33134r568141_chk"><check-content-ref href="Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux_8_STIG.xml" name="M" /><check-content>Verify if RHEL 8 is configured to audit the execution of the module management program "kmod", by running the following command:
